Error:- Constraint ${attr.plugins.cni.version.bridge} semver >= 0.4.0 filtered 1 node
Fix: Install cni and consul cni plugin, refer https://developer.hashicorp.com/nomad/docs/deploy#linux-post-installation-steps

Error:- Constraint ${attr.consul.grpc} > 0 filtered 1 node
Fix: Add below block in consul config:
ports = {
  grpc = 8502
}

Error:- Setup Failure: failed to setup alloc: pre-run hook "consul_grpc_socket" failed: 1 error occurred: * error parsing Consul address "http://127.0.0.1:8500": address http://127.0.0.1:8500: too many colons in address
Fix:- In consul block in nomad configuration add below:
consul {
  grpc_address = "127.0.0.1:8502"
}

Error:- Resources exhausted on 1 node 
Troubleshooting: free -h # on amazon linux, top command
Fix:- Increase the nomad client node resources (stop ec2, change the instance type [Actions → Instance settings → Change instance type], start the instance)
